      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This pristine specimen is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual and a factory variable M-differential. Mechanical provenance is documented, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and preventative rod bearing replacement. The chassis is reinforced with subframe plates, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. With a flawless factory finish and original Nappa leather, this M3 delivers a pure, analog driving experience with a linear power delivery and precise turn-in. A concours-level example for the discerning collector.",
